metadata.name: What happened in Jane deLila's room?
metadata.description:
When lovely Jane deLila went to sleep, little did she know about magic going on in her room at night.

While she was dreaming of cradle house, nightingales, magic street lamp and Bald Fairy Trio, golden light filled her room, and her dreams became true.

"Always have your makeup cabinet near you at night", her grandmother said to her a long time ago, "It will help you feel live and flamboyant in this grey world, and make your dreams come true!"

Grandmothers and magic go well together, don't they? ;-)
